<!--
This file contains all the mobs (monsters, NPCs, creatures, even the player. Essentially "living" things)

Related groups:
	nonspawn - Will never be generated by the game.
	nologic - No NPC logic is applied to this mob. Reserved mostly for the player.
	
	sees - Is capable of using visible perception.
	hears - Is capable of using audio perception.
	smells - Is capable of using smell perception.
	psionic - Is capable of detecting anything within range.
	
	wildlife - Fauna that randomly spawns in its respective biomes
	undead - Undead creature
	praire - Found in praires
	forest - Found in forests
	mountain - Found in mountains
-->
